# Publicação

## Imagem

POST

```http
/{INSTAGRAM_BUSINESS_ID}/media
```

Body:

```json
{
  "image_url": "",
  "caption": ""
}
```

Retorna:

```json
{
 "id": "creation_id"
}
```

Salvar:

```text
creation_id
```

---

Publicar:

POST

```http
/{INSTAGRAM_BUSINESS_ID}/media_publish
```

Body:

```json
{
 "creation_id": ""
}
```

Salvar:

```text
instagram_post_id
```

---

# Reels

POST

```http
/{INSTAGRAM_BUSINESS_ID}/media
```

